<p class="MsoNormal" dir="RTL" style="text-align: right;line-height: normal;direction: rtl"><b><span lang="AR-SY" style="font-size: 14.0pt;font-family: 'Calibri Light',sans-serif">تاريخ بداية العرض</span></b><span lang="AR-SY" style="font-size: 14.0pt;font-family: 'Calibri Light',sans-serif"> : </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size: 14.0pt;font-family: 'Calibri Light',sans-serif">05.06.2025</span></p>
