<p class="MsoNormal" dir="RTL" style="text-align: right;line-height: normal;direction: rtl"><b><span id="4" lang="AR-SY" style="font-size: 12.0pt;line-height: 105%;font-family: 'MTN Brighter Sans Arabic'">التجديد التلقائي :<span id="1" lang="AR-SY" style="font-size: 14.0pt;line-height: 105%;font-family: 'MTN Brighter Sans Arabic'"></span></span></b></p>
